    "source": "MarketWatch",
    "sourceUrl": "https://www.marketwatch.com/story/spacex-postponed-a-crucial-launch-now-its-stock-is-set-to-slide-even-further-below-the-ipo-price-143adfe0?mod=mw_rss_topstories",
